## Animation Principles
The animation system follows these principles:
1. Subtle and purposeful - enhances usability without distracting
2. Performance-optimized - uses GPU-accelerated properties
3. Responsive - adapts to different screen sizes
4. Accessible - respects user motion preferences

## Technology
This project uses Framer Motion for component animations combined with CSS transitions for simpler effects and the React Intersection Observer for scroll-triggered animations.
